# Description: Show ace-tmux session start and dynamic window add
# Tags: ace-tmux,docs,getting-started

Output docs/demo/ace-tmux-getting-started.gif

Set FontSize 16
Set Width 960
Set Height 480

Type "mise exec -- ace-tmux start default --detach"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "mise exec -- ace-tmux window cc --session default"
Enter
Sleep 2s
